        "content": "<p><span class=\"user-mention\" data-user-id=\"276696\">@Ambroise</span>, I think I agree that  <span class=\"user-mention\" data-user-id=\"277611\">@Todd Trimble</span>'s argument doesn't quite  work. Would you agree that it does work for preorders? Your example for graphs looks good to me.</p>",
